	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## LinkStash Search for Alfred

**ls {query}** — Search bookmarks, results shown in Alfred
- Enter: Open URL in browser (auto-records visit)
- Cmd+Enter: Copy URL to clipboard
- Alt+Enter: Open in LinkStash web UI

**lsweb {query}** — Open LinkStash web search in browser

Visit tracking: When you open a URL via Enter, the workflow automatically records a visit to keep your visit counts accurate across Alfred and the web UI.

### Setup
Set these Workflow Environment Variables:
- LINKSTASH_SERVER: Your server URL (e.g. https://linkstash.example.com)
- LINKSTASH_SECRET_KEY: Your authentication secret key</string>
